<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Flow xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <apiVersion>63.0</apiVersion>
    <areMetricsLoggedToDataCloud>false</areMetricsLoggedToDataCloud>
    <customErrors>
        <description>Custom Error which is shown to the user if they update the status to closed, while the work is open in Wocas.</description>
        <name>Custom_Error_Dont_Close_The_Case_Manual</name>
        <label>Custom Error - Don&apos;t Close The Case Manual</label>
        <locationX>50</locationX>
        <locationY>911</locationY>
        <customErrorMessages>
            <errorMessage>This Case is not yet closed in Wocas. If you handle the case in Wocas, the status in Salesforce will be updated automatically.</errorMessage>
            <isFieldError>false</isFieldError>
        </customErrorMessages>
    </customErrors>
    <decisions>
        <description>Has the Case Status changed?</description>
        <name>Case_Is_Reopened</name>
        <label>Case Is Reopened</label>
        <locationX>578</locationX>
        <locationY>287</locationY>
        <defaultConnector>
            <targetReference>Decision_Case_Is_Closed_With_External_Status</targetReference>
        </defaultConnector>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Reopened</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Reopened</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Update_Reopened_Case</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <doesRequireRecordChangedToMeetCriteria>true</doesRequireRecordChangedToMeetCriteria>
            <label>Reopened</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <decisions>
        <description>We don&apos;t want that users close a case if the external status is not a closed status. We check if the external status is filled and case status is changed to &apos;Closed&apos; or &apos;Closed - Accepted&apos;.</description>
        <name>Decision_Case_Is_Closed_With_External_Status</name>
        <label>Case Is Closed With External Status</label>
        <locationX>578</locationX>
        <locationY>587</locationY>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Outcome_Case_Is_Closed_With_External_Status</name>
            <conditionLogic>1 AND 2 AND (3 OR 4 OR 5)</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.External_Status__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsNull</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>false</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsChanged</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed-Accepted</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed-Rejected</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Case Is Closed With External Status</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <decisions>
        <description>If the record is found we check if the Salesforce status is &apos;Closed&apos; Or &apos;Closed - Accepted&apos;. If not we show an error. 

If the record is not found we can assume that the external status is not a closed status and we show the error as well.</description>
        <name>Wocas_Case_Status_Found_And_Not_Closed_Status</name>
        <label>Wocas Case Status Found And Not Closed Status</label>
        <locationX>314</locationX>
        <locationY>803</locationY>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Record_Found_And_Not_Closed_Status</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsNull</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>false</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status.Case_Question_Status__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>NotEqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status.Case_Request_Status__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>NotEqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed-Accepted</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status.Case_Request_Status__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>NotEqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed-Rejected</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Custom_Error_Dont_Close_The_Case_Manual</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Record Found And Not Closed Status</label>
        </rules>
        <rules>
            <name>No_Record_Found</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Wocas_Case_Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsNull</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <isGoTo>true</isGoTo>
                <targetReference>Custom_Error_Dont_Close_The_Case_Manual</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>No Record Found</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
